enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
section_title: IMPLEMENTATION OF UNFCCC ARTICLE 4.8 AND 4.9: LDCs:
sentences: LDC Expert Group Chair Bubu Pateh Jallow (The Gambia) presented outcomes from the Group's 11 th meeting and on implementation of its work programme.

David Lesolle (Botswana) will conduct informal consultations. FINANCIAL MECHANISM (CONVENTION): LDC Fund: The Secretariat reported on this item and delegates agreed that David Lesolle (Botswana) will conduct consultations.
